><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">justify-content</span>: center;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-id">#kratos-menu-wrap</span> <span class="selector-class">.sf-menu</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#ffffff</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">/* text-shadow: 0 0 10px #000000, 0 0 20px #000000, 0 0 30px #000000; */</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">10px</span> <span class="number">10px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">20px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-id">#kratos-menu-wrap</span> <span class="selector-class">.sf-menu</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">border</span>: <span class="number">2px</span> solid <span class="number">#090909</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="number">#d4d4d499</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="number">15px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-id">#kratos-desktop-topnav</span> <span class="selector-class">.sf-menu</span>&gt;<span class="selector-tag">li</span>&gt;<span class="selector-tag">ul</span><span class="selector-class">.sub-menu</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#000000</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.kratos-entry-footer</span> <span class="selector-class">.footer-tag</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#000000</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="number">#ffffff</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="number">15px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最终成果如图：</p><p><img src="pic1.png" alt="屏幕截图 2025-09-18 165919" /></p><p>于2025年9月18日17:01:49，NJU</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
